-- metadata/crashify scenario: replacement mods.lst with crashify_alpha REMOVED.
-- Copy this file over staged mods.lst to exercise stale-key cleanup:
--   cp mods-without-alpha.lst mods.lst
-- then trigger a developer-mode hot reload (Left Ctrl + Left Shift + R).
-- On the replacement generation, Relay should remove `Mod:crashify_alpha` and
-- republish only `Mod:crashify_beta` and `Mod:crashify_probe`; the
-- crashify_probe observation line should show `Mod:crashify_alpha=<absent>`
-- while the other two remain present. `ModRelay:Version` is never removed.
crashify_beta
crashify_probe
